{"id": "pos025", "name": "Audio_St07_702_10_20", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_AMB_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Sis Vicky... Are you sure this place is okay?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hmph~ Judging by my experience, this is the perfect \"Observation point\". Last time, when you were here to sneak photos of Xenon, you got busted, right? That's because the point you chose suck, rookie. You should learn from me more.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "In our current position, we look just like an average couple enjoying a meal. Ohohohoho.\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">More mother-son than couple though...</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "What did you just say!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Ow! That hurt, that hurt...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "... By the way, are you okay with this? You skipped the performance tonight, right?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Ah, no problem. They found a substitute drummer later.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "That band of yours... It seems to be going quite well.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Umm, nothing much. It's just a small band...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "If you come across any gossip about the big boys, don't forget to inform me.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "...... Oh.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "However... I certainly didn't expect you to be willing to give up your break for work. You do indeed have an abnormal enthusiasm when it comes to news about PAFF... I can smell it from a mile away.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Eh? Umm... No, there's just something...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Rest assured. I've investigated. A nobody like you has zero connection to a megastar like her.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Investigated...</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Nevertheless, it was that particular reason that made me even more curious. You don't seem to be just a fan as well. As I suspected~ You have some~ sort of~ reasoning, right? Hmmmm~?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Too close too close too close... You're scaring me...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Shh! NEKO has appeared! Take a photo now!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Eh? You're right. Okay...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "Camera shutter"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "... Did she come back herself? I don't see PAFF.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "But, it is a bit strange. The last time I came here, the windows of her room were in transparent mode. I even caught a picture of Xenon in her room... Now, it appears that we can't see what's inside.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Therefore, it means she's definitely hiding something. You still doubting my nose, eh?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Sis Vicky, you really are amazing... I feel like you can even work at the Administration Bureau. Exactly why did you come here to pursue this sort of paparazzi career...\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "... Trying too hard to dig up a girl's past won't win you any popular votes, let me tell you.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Ah! Sorry...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Hahaha! I was messing with you. Look at you, all frightened and shaking. How adorable.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Besides, what's with the \"this sort of\" paparazzi. Do you have any idea how honorable our actions are, revealing the hidden truth to the public? Ohohohoho!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Here we go again...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "Shut it! Look! The windows are open!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Ah! Got it!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "Camera shutter"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Don't seem to catch a glimpse of PAFF in this one either...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "That's fine. Take a few more photos. We'll bring them back and enlarge them. I'm absolutely not letting this exclusive report get away!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_AMB_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vickyさん……本当にこれで大丈夫なんですか？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "ふふふ……私の経験から言うわ。\nここは絶好の「観察スポット」よ。\nこの前ここでXenonを追ってる時に見つかったんでしょう？\nちっちっち…これだから新人は…場所選びがダメなのよ。\n私から学びなさい！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "こうしてれば、どこからどう見ても、カップルがご飯デートしてるようにしか見えないわ！おーっほっほっほ！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">どっちかというと親子じゃ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "何か言った！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "うあ！イタタタタ……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……それより本当に大丈夫なの？\n今日のライブドタキャンしたんでしょう？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "あぁ、大丈夫ですよ。\n代わりのドラマー見つかったんで。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あんたのバンド……最近いい感じじゃない。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "いや、そんな……\n小さなバンドですよ……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "大物のゴシップ情報掴んだら教えてよね。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……あぁ、そういうことか……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "でも……仕事のために休み返上なんて、あんたやっぱりPAFFに並々ならぬ思い入れがあるみたいねぇ？\n匂うわぁ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "えぇ？いや……別に、その、少し気になるだけです……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "大丈夫よ、安心しなさい。\n調べてみたけど、あんたみたいな地味男と大スターの間に関係なんてあるわけもなかったわ。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……調べたんだ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "でもね、だから余計に気になるのよ。\nただのファンには見えないし。\nつ・ま・り、何か理由があるんでしょ～？ん～？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "ちちち近いですって……こわいこわい……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "シッ！NEKOよ！写真！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "え？あ、ほんとだ…はい……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "シャッター"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……一人かしら？PAFFの姿が見えないわね。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "でも、やっぱり気になりますね。\nこの前来た時は、窓はクリアモードになってて、中のXenonの様子が撮れたんですけど……\n今は何も撮れませんね。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あら、あんた私の鼻を疑うって言うの？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vickyさんは本当にすごいですよ……\n管理局で仕事しても問題ないくらいです。\nなんでこんなところでゴシップ記者なんてやってるんです？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……あら、女の過去に土足で踏み込もうなんて、モテないわよ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "えぇ！す、すみません……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "ははは！冗談よ、冗談！\nビビっちゃって可愛いじゃない。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "あんた今ゴシップ記者「なんて」って言った？\n真実を民衆に伝える仕事の素晴らしさが分かってないみたいね！\nおーっほっほっほ！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "またか……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "うるさいわよ！\n見て！窓が開いたわ！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "うわ！はい！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "シャッター"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "やっぱりPAFFはいませんね……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "いいの。たくさん撮っておいて。\n帰ってから拡大して、絶対に何か掴んでやるわ！\n独占ニュースは私たちのものよ！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_AMB_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐……妳確定這邊沒問題嗎？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "哼哼～以我的經驗，這邊是絕佳的「觀察點」。你上次來這裡偷拍 Xenon 的時候被抓包了吧？那是因為你挑的點太爛了，菜鳥，跟我學著點。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "我們現在這樣，看起來就像一對正常的情侶在用餐，喔呵呵呵。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">是母子吧……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "你說什麼！？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "啊！好痛痛痛……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……話說你 OK 嗎？你把今晚的表演蹺掉了吧？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "啊，沒事，後來找到代打鼓手了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "你那個團……現在玩得不錯嘛。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "呃，沒有啦，小團而已……\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "如果沾到什麼大咖的八卦記得跟我回報啊。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……喔。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "不過……居然願意為了工作放棄假期，果然你對 PAFF 的新聞有種異常的熱衷喔……我可是聞得出來的。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "咦？呃……不，只是有點在意……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "放心吧，我查過了，你這邊緣人跟這種大明星一點關係也沒有。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……查過……</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "不過就是因為這樣，我更好奇了，你看起來也不像單純的粉絲啊，果然～是有什麼理、由、吧？哼～？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "好近好近好近……好可怕啊……\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "噓！NEKO 出現了！快拍照！\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "咦？真的耶，好……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "相機快門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……一個人回來嗎？沒看到 PAFF 呢。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "不過，真的有點奇怪，上次我來的時候房間的窗戶是透光模式，我還拍到 Xenon 了……現在好像拍不到裡面了。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "此地無銀三百兩啊，你還懷疑我的鼻子嗎？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 姐真的很厲害啊……我覺得都可以去管理局工作了，到底為什麼會跑來當這種八卦記者……\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……過度挖掘一個女人的過去，可是會不受歡迎的喔。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "啊！抱歉……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "哈哈哈！我開玩笑的啦，看你嚇成這樣，真可愛啊。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "而且你剛剛說什麼「這種」八卦記者，你還不了解我們把真相披露給大眾的行為是多麼崇高嗎？喔呵呵呵！\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "又開始了……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "閉嘴！快看！窗戶打開了！\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "啊！好！\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "相機快門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "好像也沒看到 PAFF 呢……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "沒關係，多拍幾張，回去放大輸出，我一定要搶到這則獨家！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_AMB_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "Vicky 누님……정말로 괜찮은 거예요?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "흠~ 내 경험에 의하면, 여기가 몰래 관찰하기에는 최고의 「명당」자리라고. 예전에 파파라치 하다가 Xenon한테 걸렸었지? 그건 네가 자리를 보는 눈이 없어서 그런 거라고. 그러니 잘 보고 배워두렴, 꼬마야.\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "이렇게 있으니깐 꼭 애인들이 같이 식사를 하는 것 같지? 얼마나 자연스러워~\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">엄마랑 아들이겠죠……</font>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "뭐라고 했어 지금!?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "아얏! 아으, 아파라...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "……그런데 너 이래도 괜찮은 거야? 오늘 저녁 공연도 전부 캔슬해버렸다며?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네, 괜찮아요. 대타 드러머를 구해놔서.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "네가 하는 그 밴드, 요즘 그래도 잘 나가나 보네?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "에이, 아니에요. 그냥 조그마한 밴드인데...\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "혹시라도 엄청난 빅뉴스 같은 거 물게 되면 무조건 나한테 보고해야 해!\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……네.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "그런데……설마 일을 위해 휴가까지 반납할 줄은 몰랐어. 확실히 PAFF 뉴스엔 이상하리만큼 집착하는 것 같던데...내 코를 무시하면 곤란하다고.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "네? 아... 아니에요. 그냥 조금 관심이 있어서...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "걱정 마. 사실 이미 다 찾아봤으니깐. 하긴 너랑 그런 유명한 스타랑 연결될만한 게 있을 리 없지.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……찾아봤다니……</font>\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "그래서인지 더 궁금해지더라고. 널 보면 단순히 팬심으로 집착을 보이는 건 아닌 것 같고... 과연, 무.슨.이.유.때.문.일.까.나? 흠~\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "너, 너, 너무 가깝잖아요! 무섭게...\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "앗! NEKO 다!! 빨리 찍어!\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "앗? 정말이네. 알겠어요...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "연속 촬영"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "...혼자 돌아온 건가? PAFF는 안 보이는데.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "역시 조금 이상해요. 예전엔 창문이 투명 모드로 되어 있어서 안에 있던 Xenon을 쉽게 찍을 수 있었는데...지금은 불가능할 것 같아요.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "저건 완전히 '뭔가 있답니다'라고 광고하는 꼴이라고. 아직도 내 촉이 틀렸다고 생각하는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "분명 Vicky 누님 능력은 잘 알고 있죠... 관리국 수사팀에서 일하신다 하더라도 손색이 없을 거라고 생각하니까요...그런데 어째서 이딴 가십거리를 다루는 직업을 선택하신 거예요?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "...그렇게 여자의 과거를 한꺼번에 다 캐내려고 그러면 장가 못 간다~\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "아, 죄송해요...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "하하하! 농담이라고. \n이렇게 어쩔 줄 몰라 할 땐 엄청 귀엽다니깐.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "그런데 너, 방금 「이딴」 가십거리라고 했지? 숨겨진 일을 파헤치고 진상을 대중들에게 알리는 이런 숭고한 작업을 감히 뭐!? 다시 한 번 말해봐!\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "또 시작됐군...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "닥치고 저길 봐! 창문 열었다!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "앗, 네!!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Camera_Shutter", "연속 촬영"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Hayato"], "content": "PAFF는 안 보이는 것 같은데......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Vicky"], "content": "괜찮아. 최대한 많이 찍어서 돌아가야 해. 한 장 한 장 최대한 확대해서 자세하게 살펴보면, 분명 하나쯤은 걸리는 게 있을 테니깐!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Node_AMB_01"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversa